        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down Bromley Kent</placeName>
                    <date>April 21.</date>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am very sorry that I should have troubled you when so busy &amp; when only recovering from your illness, of which I had not heard.—<ref target="#foot.f2"/> <hi rend="underline">Pray</hi> give yourself no more trouble: it is by no means worth wasting your valuable time. You did give me date of the two Chinese Encyclopedias.—<ref target="#foot.f3"/> And you have now answered some of my questions.—</p>
<p>With very sincere thanks.— Believe me | Yours very truly | C. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </div>

        

        

